author: claude-code-agent
resolution: "Implemented pm-12ib: pm update --status closed --close-reason <text> now auto-routes to pm close, returning success with warnings:['auto_routed_from_update_to_close']. Mixed updates (status+close-reason + other fields) still rejected with helpful guidance. Tests added. Reduces 248 hits/30d."
expected_result: "Expected result: closure includes explicit resolution metadata and verifiable delivery evidence."
actual_result: "Actual result: Implemented pm-12ib: pm update --status closed --close-reason <text> now auto-routes to pm close, returning success with warnings:['auto_routed_from_update_to_close']. Mixed updates (status+close-reason + other fields) still rejected with helpful guidance. Tests added. Reduces 248 hits/30d."
